/*********************************************************************** Helper Functions ***********************************************************************/
void
Split
(
const
WString
&
input
,
const
WString
&
delimiter
,
collections
::
List
<
WString
>&
fragments
) {
const
wchar_t
*
attValue
=
input
.
Buffer
();
while
(*
attValue
) {
// split the value by ';'
const
wchar_t
*
attSemicolon
=
wcsstr
(
attValue
,
delimiter
.
Buffer
());
WString
pattern
;
if
(
attSemicolon
) {
pattern
=
WString
(
attValue
,
vint
(
attSemicolon
-
attValue
));
attValue
=
attSemicolon
+
delimiter
.
Length
(); }
else
{
vint
len
=
wcslen
(
attValue
);
pattern
=
WString
(
attValue
,
len
);
attValue
+=
len
; }
fragments
.
Add
(
pattern
); } }

&

::

>&

(

,

); }

(
